messages.speech: The degree audit report allows you to keep track of the courses that apply towards your education goal such as a degree, diploma, certificate or the Minnesota Transfer Curriculum. Access Your DARS Report here: https://eservices.minnstate.edu/esession/authentication.do?campusId=304&postAuthUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fwebproc.mnscu.edu%2Feservices%2Flogin.html%3Fcampusid%3D304
